data.description: Super nice 3 bedroom, 2 bath ,2 car garage. Home is in a cul de sac and perfect for a family or someone downsizing! Home features granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, and spacious eat-in kitchen and a formal dining area for special occasions and or holidays! This space could also be utilized as an office space as well. Master bedroom on one side of home which is great for privacy, addl 2 bedrooms on the opposite side! Home is gently lived and ready for new owners! Sold AS IS where is. Agent & buyers to verify room sizes and schools.
